    Returns a string representation of this structure. The result is pretty printed in order to be easy to read. It is intended to be used for different debugging/tracing purposes, e.g. dumping structures into logging traces.

    In general no code should depend on the format of the resulting string. E.g. there must be no attempts to parse for re-creation of the original instance.

    Specified by:

    Overrides:
